item.description:

I wish to live a life with slightly higher standards. I don’t want to be a billionaire, but I’d like to have a nice steady income of at least 100k a year. I don’t want a mansion, but I would like a fairly big house. I want to live just outside of town in a rural area. I want many toys(ATV’s, dirtbikes, snowmobiles, etc). And of course, marry and have children.

Not too much to ask for, but things never go as planned.
